{
  "stem": "19596.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 85.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the compartment was full with soldiers and officers and-- going-- and leave from the front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I passed Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no civilian on that train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I passed Paris.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And maybe I should have got out in Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, I passed Paris, and all of a sudden, before the train comes in the [INAUDIBLE] line to Vichy, to unoccupied-- unoccupied France-- that was Vichy, France, who was sympathetic to [INAUDIBLE] to General [INAUDIBLE] and all that.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were picking up Jews in there too, by the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Feldgendarmerie was coming on the train to control the papers, if anybody is deserter or-- or unlawful on the train without any-- or run away from the front and sits there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, when it came to me, I showed the papers, and the passport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Was-- everything was all right, except one thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A cigarette piece of paper-- I smoked cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I rolled it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And on that cigarette piece of paper, I had a lot of addresses-- from Israel, from New York, and from London.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I put it in my-- in one of the passports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And as I showed him, it fell down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went to pick it up, and he put-- [BACKROUND NOISE] put the boot on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he picked it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about five minutes-- seven minutes later, the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was encircled by-- by an army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came on the plane with [? stolen ?] pistols.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know where to run-- the toilet?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they put me in a car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did they know who you were at that stage?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Lille.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
